<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/53317519-nine-days"><img alt="Nine Days: The Race to Save Martin Luther King Jr.&#39;s Life and Win the 1960 Election" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1605773465l/53317519._SX98_.jpg" />
